‚ÄúI‚Äôm gonna show you what the real Elvis is like tonight.‚Äù Don‚Äôt miss Austin Butler and Tom Hanks in THE film of the summer. See Baz Luhrmann‚Äôs #ElvisMovie only in theaters June 24. ‚ö°Ô∏è #TCB 

https://elvis.warnerbros.com 
https://www.facebook.com/ElvisMovie 
https://www.instagram.com/ElvisMovie 
https://twitter.com/ElvisMovie 

ELVIS is an epic, big-screen spectacle from Warner Bros. Pictures and visionary, Oscar-nominated filmmaker Baz Luhrmann that explores the life and music of Elvis Presley, starring Austin Butler and Oscar winner Tom Hanks. 

A thoroughly cinematic drama, Elvis‚Äôs (Butler) story is seen through the prism of his complicated relationship with his enigmatic manager, Colonel Tom Parker (Hanks). As told by Parker, the film delves into the complex dynamic between the two spanning over 20 years, from Presley‚Äôs rise to fame to his unprecedented stardom, against the backdrop of the evolving cultural landscape and loss of innocence in America. Central to that journey is one of the significant and influential people in Elvis‚Äôs life, Priscilla Presley (Olivia DeJonge). 

Starring alongside Butler and Hanks, award-winning theatre actress Helen Thomson (‚ÄúTop of the Lake: China Girl,‚Äù ‚ÄúRake‚Äù) plays Elvis‚Äôs mother, Gladys, Richard Roxburgh (‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù ‚ÄúBreath,‚Äù ‚ÄúHacksaw Ridge‚Äù) portrays Elvis‚Äôs father, Vernon, and DeJonge (‚ÄúThe Visit,‚Äù ‚ÄúStray Dolls‚Äù) plays Priscilla. Luke Bracey (‚ÄúHacksaw Ridge,‚Äù ‚ÄúPoint Break‚Äù) plays Jerry Schilling, Natasha Bassett (‚ÄúHail, Caesar!‚Äù) plays Dixie Locke, David Wenham (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings‚Äù Trilogy, ‚ÄúLion,‚Äù ‚Äú300‚Äù) plays Hank Snow, Kelvin Harrison Jr. (‚ÄúThe Trial of the Chicago 7,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe High Note‚Äù) plays B.B. King, Xavier Samuel (‚ÄúAdore,‚Äù ‚ÄúLove & Friendship,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Twilight Saga: Eclipse‚Äù) plays Scotty Moore, and Kodi Smit-McPhee (‚ÄúThe Power of the Dog‚Äù) plays Jimmie Rodgers Snow. 

Also in the cast, Dacre Montgomery (‚ÄúStranger Things,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Broken Heart Gallery‚Äù) plays TV director Steve Binder, alongside Australian actors Leon Ford (‚ÄúGallipoli,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Pacific‚Äù) as Tom Diskin, Kate Mulvany (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúHunters‚Äù) as Marion Keisker, Gareth Davies (‚ÄúPeter Rabbit,‚Äù ‚ÄúHunters‚Äù) as Bones Howe, Charles Grounds (‚ÄúCrazy Rich Asians,‚Äù ‚ÄúCamp‚Äù) as Billy Smith, Josh McConville (‚ÄúFantasy Island‚Äù) as Sam Phillips, and Adam Dunn (‚ÄúHome and Away‚Äù) as Bill Black. 

To play additional iconic musical artists in the film, Luhrmann cast singer/songwriter Yola as Sister Rosetta Tharpe, model Alton Mason as Little Richard, Austin, Texas native Gary Clark Jr. as Arthur Crudup, and artist Shonka Dukureh as Willie Mae ‚ÄúBig Mama‚Äù Thornton. 

Oscar nominee Luhrmann (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù) directed from a screenplay by Baz Luhrmann & Sam Bromell and Baz Luhrmann & Craig Pearce and Jeremy Doner, story by Baz Luhrmann and Jeremy Doner. The film‚Äôs producers are Luhrmann, Oscar winner Catherine Martin (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù), Gail Berman, Patrick McCormick and Schuyler Weiss. Toby Emmerich, Courtenay Valenti and Kevin McCormick executive produced. 

The director‚Äôs behind-the-scenes creative team includes director of photography Mandy Walker (‚ÄúMulan,‚Äù ‚ÄúAustralia‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer and costume designer Catherine Martin (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù), production designer Karen Murphy (‚ÄúA Star Is Born‚Äù), editors Matt Villa (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúAustralia‚Äù) and Jonathan Redmond (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù), Oscar-nominated visual effects supervisor Thomas Wood (‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù), music supervisor Anton Monsted (‚ÄúAustralia,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù) and composer Elliott Wheeler (‚ÄúThe Get Down‚Äù). 

Principal photography on ‚ÄúElvis‚Äù took place in Queensland, Australia with the support of the Queensland Government, Screen Queensland, and the Australian Government‚Äôs Producer Offset program. 

A Warner Bros. Pictures Presentation, A Bazmark Production, A Jackal Group Production, A Baz Luhrmann Film, ‚ÄúElvis‚Äù will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is set to release in theaters in North America on June 24, 2022, and internationally beginning 22 June 2022.

description:
What if funk/fusion drummer Dennis Chambers was the drummer for Tool? 

(Don‚Äôt tell Danny Carey.)

Dennis is known for his legendary backbeat and funky style. So of course we felt mischievous and we dared him to try playing ‚ÄúSchism‚Äù, one of Tool‚Äôs biggest songs. It‚Äôs full of odd time signatures, quick, complex changes and unexpected accents, and Dennis had never heard it before.

But we didn‚Äôt ask him to learn the real drum parts: we wanted to see what he‚Äôd come up with on his own after hearing the song once. While you‚Äôll hear the song with drums in this video, Dennis was actually listening to a drumless track.

‚ÄúThis is not me,‚Äù he warned us as he listened through the track, but ‚Äúin my younger days, this would‚Äôve been up my alley!‚Äù

How will Dennis Chambers not only learn a song he‚Äôs never heard before, but in a style he‚Äôs unfamiliar with ‚Äì and in odd time, at that?

Since the song doesn‚Äôt have a drum track, he listens for two things: the style and the time signature. Watch Dennis‚Äô playthrough where he gives it his own spin. It‚Äôs solid, it‚Äôs groovy, and there‚Äôs some unexpected footwork later on. It‚Äôs amazing how much a song can change with a different approach on the drums.

You‚Äôve never heard Schism played like this before!

5:40 Check out my video on other things that help promote sleep!

Sleep is so important, and I believe this remedy will help you get the sleep you need. The best natural remedy for sleep is kefir. Consume 1/2 cup of kefir before bed for better sleep. 

Kefir is similar to yogurt, but it‚Äôs better. It has more healthy, diverse microbes than yogurt. Many of these friendly microbes also survive your stomach acids, whereas the microbes in yogurt don‚Äôt.

Kefir not only has friendly bacteria but friendly yeast, too. This combination is essential. People with lactose intolerance also have an easier time digesting kefir than yogurt. 

Health benefits of kefir:
 ‚Ä¢ Decreased liver fat 
 ‚Ä¢ Fewer allergy symptoms 
 ‚Ä¢ Improved immune system 
 ‚Ä¢ Decreased inflammation 
 ‚Ä¢ Less constipation 
 ‚Ä¢ Better blood sugar 
 ‚Ä¢ Better blood pressure 
 ‚Ä¢ Decreased pathogens 

Certain microbes make serotonin. The more of the right microbes you have, the more serotonin you‚Äôll have. Serotonin is a hormone that can positively affect your mood and reduce stress. 

Kefir provides microbes that make melatonin, which is a sleep hormone. Not only that, but kefir contains microbes that make the amino acid tryptophan. Tryptophan turns into serotonin and then melatonin. 

Kefir is a good source of bioavailable calcium, which can help you get to sleep and stay asleep. The microbes in kefir also make certain B vitamins, which can greatly help with stress and calm a busy mind. The lactobacillus in kefir helps reduce cortisol, which will also help you sleep better. 

I highly recommend making your own kefir. You need something called kefir live grains (there is no grain in it) to get started. 

I like using goat milk, but you can use cow milk. The website I use to buy my kefir grains (happyherbalist.com) explains exactly how to make kefir. 

Basically, you add 1 Tbsp of the kefir grains to 1 to 2 cups of milk. Then, you set it on the counter and cover it using a cloth or paper towel and a rubber band. After 24 hours, you‚Äôll have kefir.

description:
This has been a long time coming. Anyone who watches this channel knows I love night riding, but until now I have never attempted to ride Berm Peak at night. This is due to a variety of reasons, most of which should be pretty obvious. Bike lights are designed for singletrack‚Äînot wallrides and whale tails. Tonight, we throw caution to the wind and give it a shot on my backyard mountain bike trails.

Also tonight, we‚Äôll test out some new lights from Outbound Lighting. I met the owner of the company at Sedona Mountain Bike Festival, holding down the booth all by himself. Tom is not only an entrepreneur, but an engineer, so we can be sure Outbound‚Äôs marketing department isn‚Äôt getting in the way of the important stuff. These lights were remarkably simple, free of gimmicks, very well thought out, and very bright. They also turn on and off with simple taps of the power button instead of confounding combinations that so many other manufacturers insist on. Best of all, they‚Äôre really fairly priced for what you‚Äôre getting. So I‚Äôm going to run these long term and see how they work out!

description:
Today‚Äôs Roblox In a Nutshell will be on Bee Swarm Simulator.

Roblox Bee Swarm simulator is a classic Roblox simulator game where you walk around with your bees to collect pollen and honey so you can get better equipment to get pollen and honey faster.

Like all the other Roblox simulator games, the objective is to get STRONG and RICH. To get from noob to pro, the player needs to buy more bees, improve their bee hive, buy better equipment, complete quests, kill mobs, complete challenges, and use codes to get some items. The better stuff the player gets, the more honey and pollen they will gather. The game is very grindy, just like all other simulators, and most people would use macros or scripts to farm.

There are 45 types of bees, and they all have different stats and abilities. Since the maximum number of bees a player can have is 50, they need to find the best hive build (combination of bees) to get honey fast. Rarer bees are usually higher on the tier list, and some, like the windy bee, are hard to obtain.

On top of bees, people need to grind for equipment and items like Tide Popper, Dark Scythe, Gummyballer, translator, and The Planter Of Plenty to farm more efficiently. They let the player gather more pollen, unlock new quests and drop better stuff.

This video will show you everything there is to the game. It is not a complete guide, but there are some tips you can follow to get more honey. 

Like always, this video is filled with a crap ton of dead memes in the form of funny moments/montages. Bee Swarm Simulator used to have events like the Christmas 2021 event with snowflakes and gingerbread bears, but since then, there has been no update. I hope you enjoyed this Bee Swarm Simulator video. Don‚Äôt forget to subscribe and spam E.

This trailer is a concept-mashup that shows my idea of ‚Äã‚Äãhow the teaser trailer for Poppy Playtime Chapter 3 might look like.       
____________________________________________
‚óñMade/Edited By NetPro ‚óó
‚ñª netfl.pro192@gmail.com
____________________________________________

‚óÖ On our channel we create –∞ trailer mashups ‚ñª
also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

There is no intention of infringing on anyone's intellectual property. This is not intended to deceive or defraud anyone; rather, it is intended to give fans a taste of what the film may be like. I don't own the material; I simply produce trailers for fans and others who are excited about a movie.

The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.
____________________________________________

About Poppy Playtime:

A survival horror video game with puzzle elements, developed and published by indie developer MOB Games. It was released on Steam for Windows on October 12, 2021. The game tells the story of a former employee who visits an abandoned factory of children's toys, formerly owned by the gaming company Playtime Co., 10 years after its employees disappeared without a trace.
